  <body>
    <section name="Features">
    	<ul>
    		<li>create and edit projects</li>
    		<li>share various file with your project group</li>
    		<li>manage the members of a project</li>
    		<li>append metadata to files or notes</li>
    		<li>automatically propagate local changes</li>
    		<li>automatically get the latest versions from other project members</li>
    		<li>work on files online and offline</li>
    		<li>add files or folders to the project data pool</li>
    		<li>manage the project data pool</li>
    		<li>the application supports the user to resolve version conflicts</li>
    		<li>files and notes may be organised and found in categories</li>
    		<li>find files by metadata</li>
    	</ul>
